{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CSS 物件模型 (CSSOM)","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/CSSOM","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>CSS 物件模型 (CSS Object Model, CSSOM)</strong> 是一個存放所有 CSS 選擇器與相關特性的樹狀結構容器，擁有根節點、鄰居節點、後代節點、子代節點以及其他關係。CSSCOM 非常類似於 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/DOM\">DOM 文件物件模型</a> 。它們兩者都是關鍵渲染路徑的其中一部分，是網站渲染的必要步驟。</p>\n<p>CSSOM 與 DOM 一起建構渲染樹，瀏覽器依序使用它來排版與繪製網頁。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"cssom_api","title":"CSSOM API","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/CSS_Object_Model\">CSS Object Model</a> 的系列 API 允許從 JavaScript 處理操作 CSS。它更像是 DOM，但是用於 CSS 而非 HTML。允許使用者動態讀取與修改 CSS 樣式。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"也可以看看","title":"也可以看看","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Performance/How_browsers_work\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Populating the page: how browsers work (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"也可以看看","id":"也可以看看"}],"summary":"CSS 物件模型 (CSS Object Model, CSSOM) 是一個存放所有 CSS 選擇器與相關特性的樹狀結構容器，擁有根節點、鄰居節點、後代節點、子代節點以及其他關係。CSSCOM 非常類似於 DOM 文件物件模型 。它們兩者都是關鍵渲染路徑的其中一部分，是網站渲染的必要步驟。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CSS Object Model (CSSOM)","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CSS Object Model (CSSOM)","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"CSS Object Model (CSSOM)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Modelo de Objeto CSS (CSSOM)","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"CSS Object Model (CSSOM)","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/glossary/cssom","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/glossary/cssom/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"pa